text: Wurster Nordseeküste is a municipality in Cuxhaven, in Lower Saxony, Germany. It was created on 1 January 2015 from the former municipalities of Nordholz, Cappel, Dorum, Midlum, Misselwarden, Mulsum, Padingbüttel and Wremen. == References == Category:Cuxhaven (district) Category:2015 establishments in Europe Category:2010s establishments in Germany
